1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:03,280
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:05,870
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,540 --> 00:00:09,940
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:14,650
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,550
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:21,330
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:28,300
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:28,980 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:34,860 --> 00:00:37,350
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,350 --> 00:00:39,960
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:47,740
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:51,470
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,530 --> 00:00:54,370
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:55,690
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:59,960
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,410 --> 00:01:03,090
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:06,080
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,250 --> 00:01:07,720
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:11,890
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,250 --> 00:01:22,500
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:23,930 --> 00:01:29,480
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,560
=Episode 18=

23
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,350
Thank you, Commander.

24
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,110
Last night,

25
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:31,829
I behaved too boldly.

26
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:36,660
It's nothing.

27
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,350
No one saw us anyway.

28
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,630
Even if seen, it wouldn't matter.

29
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:43,829
The Qiao couple spent
the night on a sampan.

30
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,750
If word spreads,

31
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:46,310
it'll be a romantic story.

32
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:49,950
Then we will

33
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:51,990
leave openly in the crowds

34
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:53,950
conspicuously.

35
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:02,540
Commander.

36
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:03,590
Are you alright?

37
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:06,110
It's my fault.

38
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:08,390
I lay on your arm all night

39
00:03:08,510 --> 00:03:09,790
and made your hand go numb.

40
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:11,590
It's fine. Really.

41
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,230
You don't need me

42
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:16,390
to massage it for you?

43
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,110
Stop being stubborn.

44
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:31,590
Flatbread.

45
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,190
Flatbread.

46
00:03:33,270 --> 00:03:33,870
Flatbread.

47
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,150
I want flatbread.

48
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:37,750
Sir.

49
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:39,670
Two flatbreads, please.

50
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:40,590
Alright.

51
00:03:40,710 --> 00:03:41,470
A pot of hot tea.

52
00:03:44,230 --> 00:03:44,870
Your hot tea.

53
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:45,620
Thank you.

54
00:03:45,950 --> 00:03:46,590
Your flatbreads.

55
00:03:46,950 --> 00:03:47,600
Enjoy.

56
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:06,550
Commander.

57
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:08,350
Freshly baked flatbreads.

58
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:10,430
Don't you want to try?

59
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,030
Not hungry.

60
00:04:15,070 --> 00:04:16,269
Such a stick-in-the-mud.

61
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:34,270
Unlike a Wei man.

62
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:35,909
When drinking tea earlier,

63
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,790
he added salt,

64
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:38,590
ginger,

65
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:39,670
and pepper.

66
00:04:39,710 --> 00:04:40,230
Exactly.

67
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,950
That's a Wutuo custom.

68
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,430
It's used to fight

69
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:44,350
the cold.

70
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:12,990
This Wutuo man

71
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:14,190
has accomplices.

72
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:15,790
They're leaving the city.

73
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:17,270
Should we follow?

74
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:23,590
Look at those two.

75
00:05:27,590 --> 00:05:29,110
Though the girl is coughing violently,

76
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:30,390
her grandmother

77
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:31,390
shows no concern.

78
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,190
She's gripping the girl's hand

79
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:35,110
like fearing an escape.

80
00:05:35,550 --> 00:05:36,670
That old woman's suspicious.

81
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:38,110
Intercept her.

82
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:40,870
Stop!

83
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:47,909
Hand over the girl.

84
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,270
Surrender quietly,

85
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:51,710
and I'll spare your life.

86
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,390
If I can't take this girl,

87
00:05:54,710 --> 00:05:56,350
she'll die here.

88
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,710
These Wutuo people are cunning.

89
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:29,510
He.

90
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:31,510
Master.

91
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,590
Let's leave first.

92
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:35,950
Follow me.

93
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:43,670
Master, what happened earlier?

94
00:06:44,110 --> 00:06:45,150
Who's this girl?

95
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:46,430
That old woman

96
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:47,710
was a Wutuo spy

97
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:48,830
infiltrating Jiyang.

98
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:49,870
I've been

99
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:50,909
tracking them

100
00:06:50,909 --> 00:06:51,830
for some time.

101
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:53,830
This child

102
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,230
is Princess Mengji's daughter.

103
00:06:55,909 --> 00:06:57,550
They nearly abducted her earlier.

104
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,430
No wonder Cui Yuezhi's frantic.

105
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:01,070
I'll return first

106
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:02,310
to report finding

107
00:07:02,470 --> 00:07:04,070
the kid and the Wutuo spies.

108
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:05,750
Go with your master

109
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:06,590
to escort the kid.

110
00:07:11,150 --> 00:07:11,910
Stay vigilant.

111
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:20,720
(Herbal Apothecary)

112
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:32,870
To locate

113
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:33,830
that injured Wutuo man,

114
00:07:34,110 --> 00:07:35,470
we searched many apothecaries

115
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,230
but found no trace.

116
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,100
No rush.

117
00:07:38,550 --> 00:07:39,190
He must still be

118
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:40,470
in Jiyang.

119
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,810
(Herb Names)

120
00:08:02,150 --> 00:08:03,230
That's him.

121
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:06,430
Follow him.

122
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:28,070
I was wondering earlier

123
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:30,510
why the Wutuo people spared me.

124
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,220
(Xu)

125
00:08:35,309 --> 00:08:36,150
Later, I found out

126
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,150
it was

127
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:38,070
because they saw

128
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:39,350
the Xu token.

129
00:08:40,190 --> 00:08:40,909
Judging by this,

130
00:08:41,309 --> 00:08:42,950
they are connected to Chancellor Xu,

131
00:08:43,190 --> 00:08:44,790
perhaps even acting under his orders.

132
00:08:47,110 --> 00:08:48,310
For Chai Anxi,

133
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:50,030
so many Wutuo agents have come here.

134
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:51,550
I fear Jiyang City

135
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,230
is headed for turmoil.

136
00:08:53,600 --> 00:09:00,590
(Cloudbird Manor)

137
00:09:03,830 --> 00:09:04,710
Cloudbird Manor?

138
00:09:05,590 --> 00:09:06,870
Master, why here?

139
00:09:07,230 --> 00:09:08,590
This child's been drugged.

140
00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:09,790
I must go inside

141
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,830
to prepare an antidote.

142
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:12,190
Bring her

143
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:13,030
and follow me in.

144
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:37,750
Earlier,

145
00:09:37,950 --> 00:09:39,310
who was that gentleman?

146
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,490
Also,

147
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,190
why change into women's clothes?

148
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:47,990
He's General Fengyun, Xiao Jue.

149
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:49,510
We came to Jiyang

150
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:50,630
on official business.

151
00:09:51,310 --> 00:09:52,390
As for the clothing change,

152
00:09:52,950 --> 00:09:54,070
it's to conceal my identity.

153
00:09:56,590 --> 00:09:58,510
So that's General Fengyun.

154
00:09:59,710 --> 00:10:00,790
No wonder he immediately

155
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:02,030
started giving you orders.

156
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,070
He's the Right Army Commander.

157
00:10:05,430 --> 00:10:06,190
I'm just one

158
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:06,870
of his soldiers.

159
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:08,390
Of course he can order me.

160
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:12,070
You seem quite protective of him.

161
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:13,520
What?

162
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:14,590
Do you like him?

163
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:25,590
Between us,

164
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,870
there's indeed some history.

165
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,470
But my own path

166
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,190
is not yet clear.

167
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,470
I suppose

168
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:36,830
nothing will come of it.

169
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,750
Let me divine

170
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:42,510
your fates.

171
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:25,990
The hexagram is Kan.

172
00:11:26,950 --> 00:11:27,950
It represents water.

173
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:29,670
From peril to greater peril.

174
00:11:30,110 --> 00:11:31,190
Trapped between dangers

175
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:32,390
with no escape in sight.

176
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:34,590
Does this mean

177
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,070
being with him would bring

178
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:38,590
certain disaster?

179
00:11:44,230 --> 00:11:45,190
Remember what I said

180
00:11:45,190 --> 00:11:46,110
earlier?

181
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:47,790
It signifies danger,

182
00:11:48,230 --> 00:11:49,990
but water is adaptable.

183
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,750
Navigate through hazards

184
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:53,470
and find passage in peril.

185
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:58,830
Human conquers fate.

186
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,510
Don't bow to destiny.

187
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:54,430
That melody sounds so familiar.

188
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:56,510
My mother often plays this

189
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:58,150
in her leisure time.

190
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,150
I think it's called

191
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:02,270
Slow Passing Years.

192
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:12,110
(Cloudbird Manor)

193
00:13:23,430 --> 00:13:25,310
(Clouds and birds fade from memory.)

194
00:13:26,270 --> 00:13:28,870
(One day, we'll reunite
at the city tower.)

195
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:30,870
(Cloudbird Manor.)

196
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:32,990
(So that's how it is.)

197
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:41,220
(Cloudbird Manor)

198
00:13:48,070 --> 00:13:48,790
Mr. Cui,

199
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:50,150
you've finally arrived.

200
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:54,950
Sorry for the delay.

201
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,750
Are you okay?

202
00:13:57,430 --> 00:13:57,950
I nearly

203
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:58,830
came close to

204
00:13:58,830 --> 00:13:59,750
being killed.

205
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,710
Mr. Liu saved me.

206
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:05,870
I'm Cui Yuezhi.

207
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:07,150
My deepest gratitude

208
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,790
for saving the little princess.

209
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,470
Thanks to your information

210
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,030
about the Wutuo spies,

211
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:12,990
I've sent people

212
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,110
to catch them.

213
00:14:14,510 --> 00:14:15,230
It was nothing.

214
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:16,630
Don't mention it.

215
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:17,910
You'd better return

216
00:14:18,470 --> 00:14:19,590
with the little princess.

217
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:20,550
We shouldn't let

218
00:14:20,950 --> 00:14:22,030
her elders worry.

219
00:14:22,790 --> 00:14:23,470
Of course.

220
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:25,270
I should report this

221
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:26,350
to Princess Mengji.

222
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:27,670
Would you

223
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:28,510
accompany me?

224
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,350
When she learns

225
00:14:30,350 --> 00:14:31,750
of your heroic deed,

226
00:14:32,350 --> 00:14:34,150
she'll surely reward you generously.

227
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,550
I avoid worldly ties.

228
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:37,550
No need.

229
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:39,590
Alright, alright.

230
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:41,470
Your Highness.

231
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:42,480
After you.

232
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:45,950
Mr. Liu.

233
00:14:46,310 --> 00:14:47,030
Visit me sometime.

234
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:57,070
He.

235
00:14:57,830 --> 00:14:58,470
You two

236
00:14:58,750 --> 00:14:59,510
may return.

237
00:14:59,950 --> 00:15:00,590
Be careful.

238
00:15:01,950 --> 00:15:02,630
- Yes.
- Yes.

239
00:15:12,470 --> 00:15:13,100
What's wrong?

240
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:15,230
Your master

241
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,350
cares a lot about the little princess.

242
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:21,270
He rarely speaks of the past.

243
00:15:22,190 --> 00:15:23,430
But I can sense

244
00:15:23,950 --> 00:15:25,710
he harbors many regrets in his heart

245
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:26,830
and sorrows.

246
00:15:28,430 --> 00:15:29,790
I don't want to see him sad.

247
00:15:30,350 --> 00:15:30,910
That's why

248
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:33,150
I never mention it.

249
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:41,510
(Mengji Mansion, Jiyang)

250
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:46,020
(Cultivate Virtue)

251
00:15:58,110 --> 00:15:58,870
The little princess

252
00:15:59,070 --> 00:16:00,310
entered to see Princess Mengji.

253
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:01,470
We'll wait here

254
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:03,030
for her summons.

255
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:04,790
Uncle.

256
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:06,070
Tell us

257
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:07,030
about Princess Mengji,

258
00:16:07,430 --> 00:16:08,670
so we don't offend her later.

259
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,190
Back then,

260
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:14,710
the old lord had a son and a daughter.

261
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:18,150
The eldest son died before 18.

262
00:16:18,990 --> 00:16:20,390
In those days, the Mengji Mansion

263
00:16:20,430 --> 00:16:22,550
was like a boat in stormy seas.

264
00:16:23,270 --> 00:16:24,910
To stabilize the situation, the Princess

265
00:16:25,230 --> 00:16:26,990
married the son
of a high-ranking official.

266
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:28,670
After her husband's death,

267
00:16:29,070 --> 00:16:30,430
she took charge of governance,

268
00:16:30,710 --> 00:16:31,870
quelled internal conflicts,

269
00:16:32,350 --> 00:16:33,230
won over the people,

270
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:34,910
and steered

271
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:36,830
Jiyang's slow return to stability.

272
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:41,630
The Princess arrives!

273
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:04,109
(Mu Hongjin, Princess Mengji)

274
00:17:04,670 --> 00:17:05,990
I'm Cui Yuezhi.

275
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:07,310
Your Highness.

276
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:08,910
Huanqing, Yuyan,

277
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:10,190
greet the Princess.

278
00:17:14,829 --> 00:17:15,829
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

279
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:19,190
Mr. Cui.

280
00:17:19,790 --> 00:17:20,550
These two

281
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,349
are your long-lost nephew

282
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:24,069
and niece-in-law?

283
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:26,109
Your Highness,

284
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:27,390
this young man

285
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:29,230
is my nephew, Huanqing.

286
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:30,590
Beside him

287
00:17:30,630 --> 00:17:32,110
stands this lovely and dutiful lady,

288
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,750
his recently wedded wife,

289
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:34,430
Yuyan.

290
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,710
Huanqing

291
00:17:36,950 --> 00:17:39,230
is handsome, clever, and skilled in

292
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:40,630
both civil and martial arts.

293
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:42,390
His demeanor

294
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:44,710
greatly resembles my late elder brother.

295
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:46,230
Every time I see him,

296
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:49,630
I'm filled with melancholy.

297
00:17:50,350 --> 00:17:51,670
I never realized

298
00:17:52,190 --> 00:17:53,910
the Right Army Commander had free time

299
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,270
to impersonate someone

300
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:58,550
to come to my place?

301
00:18:05,710 --> 00:18:06,870
You old fool.

302
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:09,190
Falling for such an obvious deception.

303
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:11,110
He resembles your dead brother?

304
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:12,910
Have you looked in a mirror?

305
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,910
Your family

306
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,670
are never known

307
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:17,990
for handsomeness.

308
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:18,610
I...

309
00:18:22,990 --> 00:18:24,430
Please stop

310
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:25,790
beating around the bush.

311
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:27,790
Why did you infiltrate Jiyang City?

312
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:30,270
What's your true purpose?

313
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:32,590
My apologies, Your Highness.

314
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:34,750
My visit here

315
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:36,510
aims to find someone.

316
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:38,510
Chai Anxi,

317
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:40,390
once my father's subordinate,

318
00:18:40,990 --> 00:18:42,470
went missing in the Mingshui Battle.

319
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:44,830
After tracking him all this way,

320
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,430
I had no choice

321
00:18:46,910 --> 00:18:47,830
but to hide my identity

322
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:48,910
to enter Jiyang.

323
00:18:49,990 --> 00:18:51,750
Mr. Cui was kept in the dark.

324
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:53,430
Your Highness,

325
00:18:53,630 --> 00:18:54,470
please forgive him.

326
00:18:55,830 --> 00:18:57,390
Is that your excuse?

327
00:18:57,830 --> 00:18:58,590
Do you know

328
00:18:58,990 --> 00:18:59,870
nowadays, Jiyang

329
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:01,830
has been infiltrated

330
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:02,750
by many Wutuo spies?

331
00:19:04,190 --> 00:19:05,110
Is this true?

332
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,350
Jiyang City is impenetrable.

333
00:19:07,870 --> 00:19:09,110
How did they infiltrate?

334
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:10,910
Your Highness,

335
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:12,830
as General Xiao mentioned,

336
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:13,750
the Wutuo people

337
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:15,150
used unknown methods

338
00:19:15,390 --> 00:19:16,430
to infiltrate Jiyang City.

339
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:19,070
They ambushed the little princess

340
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:20,510
during her outing,

341
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:21,590
probably

342
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:22,710
to blackmail you.

343
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,470
Please don't worry.

344
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:26,270
I've deployed people to capture

345
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,510
the Wutuo spies.

346
00:19:28,150 --> 00:19:29,350
Given current circumstances,

347
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:31,110
merely catching them

348
00:19:31,670 --> 00:19:32,390
won't suffice.

349
00:19:32,870 --> 00:19:33,950
What's your proposal?

350
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:35,350
As you said,

351
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:37,150
Jiyang is impenetrable

352
00:19:37,470 --> 00:19:38,270
as the world knows.

353
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,430
But now,

354
00:19:40,190 --> 00:19:41,390
the Wutuo agents have managed

355
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:42,670
to infiltrate effortlessly

356
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:44,670
and target the little princess.

357
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:46,030
This proves

358
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,070
their actions are premeditated

359
00:19:48,910 --> 00:19:49,990
and well-prepared.

360
00:19:51,630 --> 00:19:52,210
Your Highness,

361
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:54,550
for Jiyang's citizens' safety,

362
00:19:55,150 --> 00:19:56,470
we must prepare early

363
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:57,670
and take precautions.

364
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,790
This is our business.

365
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:02,350
We'll handle it ourselves.

366
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:09,110
Your Highness,

367
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:11,110
Military Inspector Chu Zhao is outside.

368
00:20:13,910 --> 00:20:14,590
Let him in.

369
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:30,310
Your Highness.

370
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,670
Skip formalities.

371
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:33,710
Why would a military inspector

372
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:35,870
visit Jiyang?

373
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,830
Are you sent by the court?

374
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,150
You misunderstand.

375
00:20:40,470 --> 00:20:41,590
I'm returning to the capital

376
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:43,190
and merely passing through.

377
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:46,230
Then why request this meeting?

378
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,350
I

379
00:20:48,630 --> 00:20:50,110
spotted a Wutuo spy.

380
00:20:59,110 --> 00:20:59,710
Where?

381
00:21:00,670 --> 00:21:01,550
At an herb shop.

382
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:02,870
A wounded man had

383
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:04,430
a wolf-head tattoo

384
00:21:04,950 --> 00:21:05,670
on his right arm,

385
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:07,510
a Wutuo identifier,

386
00:21:07,630 --> 00:21:08,670
revealed during treatment.

387
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:10,390
I tracked him

388
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:12,430
to a group of Wutuo spies.

389
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:14,070
There were over a dozen.

390
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,310
Clearly,

391
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:17,790
multiple Wutuo groups

392
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,670
have infiltrated

393
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:20,070
this city.

394
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:22,670
Please reconsider

395
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:24,070
my proposal,

396
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:26,470
Your Highness.

397
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,830
We appreciate your warning.

398
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:30,670
But we'll handle

399
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:33,030
our own affairs.

400
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:34,230
You may leave.

401
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:36,470
Host them at the mansion tonight.

402
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:52,580
(Self-Revealing Virtue)

403
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:57,270
Mr. Qiao?

404
00:21:59,150 --> 00:22:00,470
I didn't expect you in Jiyang

405
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:01,790
under a new name.

406
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:03,550
There's more.

407
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,190
I've even gotten married.

408
00:22:07,550 --> 00:22:08,110
Mr. Chu,

409
00:22:08,630 --> 00:22:09,670
we're destined to meet

410
00:22:09,950 --> 00:22:10,790
wherever we go.

411
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,190
Putting it that way,

412
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:15,470
it seems we're always reuniting.

413
00:22:15,910 --> 00:22:17,350
Then you must be very busy, Mr. Chu.

414
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:18,750
Even crossing a street

415
00:22:19,150 --> 00:22:20,190
would make you reunite

416
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:21,430
with many 'destined ones'.

417
00:22:31,870 --> 00:22:33,110
Commander, night approaches.

418
00:22:33,310 --> 00:22:34,190
Let's dine.

419
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,710
Xiao Jue's arrival was abrupt

420
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,710
and impolite.

421
00:22:50,150 --> 00:22:51,390
But a general of his caliber

422
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:52,710
never acts rashly.

423
00:22:53,230 --> 00:22:54,270
Mobilize defenses,

424
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:56,110
increase patrols and drills,

425
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:57,350
and stockpile herbs

426
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,190
just in case.

427
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:00,230
Understood.

428
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:01,390
Moreover,

429
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:03,310
he saved Lou.

430
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:05,430
Keep his presence here

431
00:23:05,670 --> 00:23:06,430
confidential.

432
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:08,350
Help his search

433
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:09,710
for the person.

434
00:23:11,470 --> 00:23:12,050
Yes.

435
00:23:18,690 --> 00:23:23,600
(Self-Revealing Virtue)

436
00:23:48,390 --> 00:23:49,310
Slow Passing Years.

437
00:24:14,270 --> 00:24:15,150
Your Highness.

438
00:24:16,950 --> 00:24:17,790
Slow Passing Years.

439
00:24:19,030 --> 00:24:20,670
Have you heard this song?

440
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:23,390
My master often plays it.

441
00:24:26,230 --> 00:24:28,390
I heard Lou mention it.

442
00:24:28,910 --> 00:24:29,590
Her savior

443
00:24:30,150 --> 00:24:31,590
also included a white-clad hero

444
00:24:32,150 --> 00:24:33,190
with a sword in hand

445
00:24:33,390 --> 00:24:34,630
and a zither on his back.

446
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:36,710
Do you know

447
00:24:37,510 --> 00:24:38,430
who he might be?

448
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:41,310
That was my master

449
00:24:41,710 --> 00:24:43,670
Liu Buwang, the Cloudforest Hermit.

450
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:48,670
Liu Buwang?

451
00:24:51,190 --> 00:24:51,990
Is he well?

452
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:55,020
No.

453
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:56,990
No need to tell me.

454
00:24:57,990 --> 00:24:58,790
I don't care.

455
00:25:03,670 --> 00:25:04,790
May I ask you

456
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,430
if you

457
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:08,230
and my master

458
00:25:09,390 --> 00:25:10,590
were once acquainted?

459
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,350
(Many years ago,)

460
00:25:17,390 --> 00:25:18,510
(to escape my marriage,)

461
00:25:19,670 --> 00:25:21,030
(I secretly fled the mansion.)

462
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:29,430
Run faster, little lady!

463
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:31,600
- Try running!
- Where can you flee now?

464
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:33,990
Help! Is anyone there to save me?

465
00:25:34,230 --> 00:25:34,910
Run!

466
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:36,350
Scream!

467
00:25:36,470 --> 00:25:37,630
Yeah, keep running!

468
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:55,020
Sir.

469
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:56,550
Help me, sir!

470
00:25:57,190 --> 00:25:58,350
Carrying a zither?

471
00:25:59,150 --> 00:26:00,030
You fragile man

472
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:01,590
want to be a hero?

473
00:26:01,990 --> 00:26:02,590
Scram.

474
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:04,510
Sir.

475
00:26:05,550 --> 00:26:06,190
Still here?

476
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:07,390
Get him!

477
00:26:23,190 --> 00:26:23,950
Sir.

478
00:26:46,150 --> 00:26:47,030
Thank you.

479
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:48,750
I'm Mu Hongjin.

480
00:26:49,190 --> 00:26:50,270
What's your name?

481
00:26:52,870 --> 00:26:53,510
Liu Buwang.

482
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:54,950
If you're unharmed,

483
00:26:55,190 --> 00:26:56,190
I'll take my leave.

484
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,430
Mr. Liu.

485
00:27:01,670 --> 00:27:03,270
I think my ankle's sprained.

486
00:27:04,230 --> 00:27:05,070
In for a penny,

487
00:27:05,430 --> 00:27:06,310
in for a pound.

488
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:07,550
How about

489
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:09,150
you carry me?

490
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:09,900
No.

491
00:27:10,910 --> 00:27:11,550
That's improper.

492
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,830
It really does hurt

493
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,270
when I move.

494
00:27:21,190 --> 00:27:22,750
Please, sir.

495
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:32,560
Miss,

496
00:27:32,990 --> 00:27:33,710
where's your home?

497
00:27:34,350 --> 00:27:35,150
I'll take you back.

498
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:36,310
I have no home.

499
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:38,150
I was kidnapped and brought here.

500
00:27:38,710 --> 00:27:40,750
My home is very far away.

501
00:27:41,390 --> 00:27:42,470
I'll follow you.

502
00:27:42,790 --> 00:27:44,190
Wherever you go, I go.

503
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:45,750
What do you mean

504
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:46,550
by "follow me"?

505
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,350
Why would you follow me?

506
00:27:49,230 --> 00:27:50,430
Since you saved me,

507
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:51,990
see it through to the end.

508
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,950
Or escort me home.

509
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,430
My home is far away.

510
00:27:56,670 --> 00:27:57,350
Can you do it?

511
00:27:57,470 --> 00:27:58,060
Of course.

512
00:27:59,870 --> 00:28:01,150
My home's in Yaojing.

513
00:28:04,870 --> 00:28:05,710
Don't worry.

514
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:06,950
I don't eat much.

515
00:28:07,030 --> 00:28:08,430
I won't cost you much.

516
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,350
Having me along

517
00:28:09,470 --> 00:28:10,590
won't be a burden.

518
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:12,190
No.

519
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:16,270
Please, please.

520
00:28:19,230 --> 00:28:20,670
I'm begging you.

521
00:28:42,830 --> 00:28:43,430
Thank you.

522
00:29:39,510 --> 00:29:40,270
I'm starving.

523
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:41,550
Sir.

524
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,870
Can we have a proper meal?

525
00:29:44,510 --> 00:29:45,040
No.

526
00:29:45,430 --> 00:29:46,230
After a month,

527
00:29:46,630 --> 00:29:47,790
my money is nearly gone.

528
00:29:49,910 --> 00:29:51,830
Candied haws for sale!

529
00:29:53,790 --> 00:29:54,630
Candied haws.

530
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:55,390
Want one?

531
00:29:56,150 --> 00:29:56,750
Take a look.

532
00:30:01,630 --> 00:30:02,990
Sir, one please.

533
00:30:03,390 --> 00:30:04,310
Alright. Thank you.

534
00:30:05,430 --> 00:30:06,190
Here, hold this.

535
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:17,030
You still care about me.

536
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:17,910
Want some?

537
00:30:19,030 --> 00:30:19,550
Miss.

538
00:30:20,390 --> 00:30:20,940
Boundaries.

539
00:30:30,390 --> 00:30:31,590
Take a bouquet if you like it.

540
00:30:31,910 --> 00:30:32,510
This one, then.

541
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:33,310
Take care.

542
00:30:37,910 --> 00:30:38,990
This looks nice.

543
00:30:40,710 --> 00:30:42,790
These bracelets
are called Joyful Hearts.

544
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,510
My husband and I

545
00:30:44,630 --> 00:30:45,630
carved them together.

546
00:30:46,430 --> 00:30:47,670
Joyful Hearts bracelets.

547
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:49,150
Any special meaning?

548
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:50,310
If lovers

549
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,790
wear these bracelets,

550
00:30:53,030 --> 00:30:54,390
they'll never be separated.

551
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:58,150
Is this your lover?

552
00:30:59,030 --> 00:31:00,470
Buy a pair for the lady.

553
00:31:00,750 --> 00:31:01,550
A lifetime

554
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:02,950
of togetherness.

555
00:31:03,870 --> 00:31:04,870
You heard that, Mr. Liu?

556
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:06,430
Buy me one?

557
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:21,230
She's not my lover.

558
00:31:28,470 --> 00:31:30,030
- Great!
- Great!

559
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:30,910
You sure

560
00:31:30,950 --> 00:31:32,310
I'm not your lover?

561
00:31:37,870 --> 00:31:38,750
No flowers?

562
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:40,350
No.

563
00:31:53,710 --> 00:31:54,270
It's me.

564
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:07,670
Soldiers are everywhere outside,

565
00:32:07,870 --> 00:32:08,670
checking everyone.

566
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:10,390
Seemingly searching for someone.

567
00:32:15,430 --> 00:32:16,190
Tomorrow,

568
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,790
I must return to Qiyun Mountain.

569
00:32:19,950 --> 00:32:21,350
Will you come with me?

570
00:32:21,870 --> 00:32:22,990
You'll meet my master.

571
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:25,910
I can't go with you.

572
00:32:30,470 --> 00:32:30,990
Why?

573
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:33,870
I'm Prince Mengji's daughter.

574
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:37,070
The person those soldiers are hunting

575
00:32:38,230 --> 00:32:38,990
is me.

576
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,230
My father wants

577
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:42,350
me to marry

578
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,670
a court official's son

579
00:32:44,630 --> 00:32:46,150
to strengthen his political standing.

580
00:32:47,390 --> 00:32:47,910
I refused.

581
00:32:47,950 --> 00:32:48,910
That's why I fled.

582
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:50,910
But then I met you.

583
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,190
This past month

584
00:32:54,190 --> 00:32:55,870
has been truly joyful.

585
00:32:59,630 --> 00:33:00,350
Mr. Liu,

586
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,430
I don't want that marriage.

587
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:05,590
But I can't go up the mountain with you.

588
00:33:06,510 --> 00:33:07,470
What should I do?

589
00:33:11,710 --> 00:33:12,270
In that case,

590
00:33:12,910 --> 00:33:14,270
wait here at this inn.

591
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:15,590
I'll go

592
00:33:15,950 --> 00:33:17,150
tell my master

593
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:18,710
and then return in two days.

594
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:20,230
We'll resolve this together.

595
00:33:22,270 --> 00:33:23,430
Must you leave now?

596
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,190
I'll definitely return.

597
00:33:25,950 --> 00:33:26,510
Liu Buwang,

598
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:29,910
remember your promise.

599
00:33:31,670 --> 00:33:32,710
You must come back.

600
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,230
I will.

601
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:21,840
♪Through endless nights, I walk alone♪

602
00:34:22,050 --> 00:34:25,690
♪Heartache swirls like ceaseless winds♪

603
00:34:29,830 --> 00:34:32,659
♪Yet I yearn to stand opposed to you♪

604
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:36,560
♪Seeking fleeting clarity♪

605
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:40,820
