♪I'm shrouded in darkness♪

613
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:06,300
♪Resent old dreams like drifting clouds♪

614
00:35:06,580 --> 00:35:08,400
♪Fading into oblivion♪

615
00:35:08,790 --> 00:35:09,790
I just want to know

616
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:12,710
