632
00:35:45,430 --> 00:35:46,950
My master isn't like that.

633
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,830
There must be reasons.

634
00:35:54,350 --> 00:35:56,350
Time only hastens aging,

635
00:35:57,630 --> 00:35:58,790
