637
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:41,090
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

638
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:45,120
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

639
00:36:45,290 --> 00:36:47,240
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

640
00:36:47,330 --> 00:36:52,260
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

641
00:37:04,350 --> 00:37:05,760
